sectionname: Introduction
startweek: 35
endweek: 43

The main themes in the 1 semester introduction period are: Robolab, Networking, Interfacing, linguistic communication, data communication and Mathematics. The student will for the first 8 weeks meet problems within the two specialization subjects Networking and Electronics, in order to be able to choose the proper specialization area as well as learning about both areas in order to convey flexibility in future projects. 

Each project will be connected to the theoretical teaching in the classes
